1
00:00:09,750 --> 00:00:12,270
Qingcheng Public Security Bureau
fallen detective Tang Zhigang.

2
00:00:12,670 --> 00:00:13,880
Badge number reactivated.

3
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:16,160
Passed down to his son, Tang Tang.

4
00:00:25,190 --> 00:00:27,640
Badge No. 030023.

5
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:30,600
Yes, sir!

6
00:00:31,920 --> 00:00:32,840
Welcome back.

7
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:34,110
Welcome back.

8
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:35,360
Welcome back.

9
00:00:35,640 --> 00:00:36,640
Welcome back.

10
00:00:37,750 --> 00:00:38,590
Salute.

11
00:00:54,060 --> 00:00:57,940
=The Hidden Truth=

12
00:00:57,940 --> 00:01:00,580
=Episode 12=

13
00:01:07,870 --> 00:01:08,710
Where's Tang Tang?

14
00:01:11,350 --> 00:01:12,190
He didn't come.

15
00:01:23,980 --> 00:01:28,900
(Martyr Zhao Fengcheng.
In loving memory, by Tang Tang)

16
00:01:28,900 --> 00:01:33,980
(Maojian tea)

17
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,920
Hats off.

18
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,520
Bow.

19
00:02:20,030 --> 00:02:21,030
Second bow.

20
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,430
Third bow.

21
00:02:28,190 --> 00:02:29,030
Hats on.

22
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:32,470
Salute.

23
00:02:40,140 --> 00:02:42,580
(Maojian tea)

24
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:49,020
(Criminal Investigation Team 2)

25
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:50,920
Captain Zhao...

26
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:37,710
Is Li Xu's interrogation setup ready?

27
00:03:38,590 --> 00:03:40,120
All set. You want to handle it?

28
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:45,840
I'll take it.

29
00:03:49,180 --> 00:03:53,580
(Qingcheng Public Security Bureau)

30
00:03:58,470 --> 00:03:59,750
Just you here?

31
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,240
Where's the old man?

32
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,150
You've really got some luck?

33
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,000
Fell from that height,

34
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,800
I thought you'd be dead or crippled.

35
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:14,590
Disappointed?

36
00:04:16,190 --> 00:04:17,190
Not really.

37
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:18,950
Since you're alive,

38
00:04:20,070 --> 00:04:20,910
I'll go easy.

39
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:23,880
Alright.

40
00:04:24,630 --> 00:04:25,870
You've thought things through.

41
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,720
If that's the case,

42
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,480
let's have a proper talk.

43
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,560
Maybe you'll get off lighter.

44
00:04:37,680 --> 00:04:38,680
I'll confess.

45
00:04:39,630 --> 00:04:41,720
I took people to beat Wang Li.

46
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:43,120
We had beef.

47
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,310
He owed me money.

48
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:45,950
I beat him,

49
00:04:45,950 --> 00:04:46,920
but nobody died.

50
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,290
A few days inside, that's it.

51
00:04:52,190 --> 00:04:53,310
I overrated you.

52
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,270
Let me remind you.

53
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,720
Last Thursday,

54
00:04:57,950 --> 00:04:59,920
you, Zhang Ming, and Wang Li

55
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,830
were all at Hongyun.

56
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,120
What were you doing?

57
00:05:03,150 --> 00:05:04,120
What did you talk about?

58
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:07,120
Wang Li was handing the restaurant to me.

59
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,480
My people have already moved in.

60
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:10,630
We're redecorating.

61
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,560
Anyone else there?

62
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:14,070
No. Just us.

63
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:18,960
What about him?.

64
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,830
Take a good look.

65
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:27,950
I told you. I don't know him.

66
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:29,070
Stop bluffing

67
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:30,390
and acting like a grownup.

68
00:05:36,830 --> 00:05:38,310
You know what he did?

69
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:40,270
I said I don't know him.

70
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:42,510
What he did is none of my business.

71
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,830
He's a big deal.

72
00:05:47,810 --> 00:05:49,560
The main culprit in the Naked Banquet Case

73
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,120
and Liu Yan's case.

74
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,830
On the run for over ten years.

75
00:05:56,310 --> 00:05:57,720
Multiple deaths on him.

76
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,920
And now you're tied to him.

77
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,120
You think we have no evidence?

78
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:07,270
If you say nothing,

79
00:06:07,270 --> 00:06:08,390
that's harboring.

80
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,270
He's facing the death penalty.

81
00:06:11,430 --> 00:06:12,270
You?

82
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:15,760
Well,

83
00:06:16,950 --> 00:06:17,950
I suggest

84
00:06:18,630 --> 00:06:20,190
you appreciate that I'm sitting here,

85
00:06:20,190 --> 00:06:21,680
talking to you nicely.

86
00:06:28,630 --> 00:06:29,750
I want to see Officer Tang.

87
00:06:32,070 --> 00:06:33,480
Officer Tang!

88
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,960
Stop yelling.

89
00:06:39,260 --> 00:06:40,820
(Tang Tang: I'll interrogate Wang Li.)

90
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,040
You say we know each other.

91
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,000
Where's the proof?

92
00:06:50,750 --> 00:06:51,800
If you've got it, show me.

93
00:06:52,510 --> 00:06:54,190
We don't have

94
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:55,830
photos of you together.

95
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,430
But whether Bai

96
00:06:57,430 --> 00:06:58,720
kept something on you,

97
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,870
that I don't know.

98
00:07:01,630 --> 00:07:02,950
What do fifteen years ago

99
00:07:02,950 --> 00:07:04,310
have to do with me?

100
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:07,000
And that banquet thing.

101
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:07,950
I know nothing.

102
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:09,270
Go interrogate him.

103
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:13,000
You don't want to talk to me?

104
00:07:13,630 --> 00:07:14,470
I...

105
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:17,880
Tang Tang.

106
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,830
We've got Bai.

107
00:07:19,830 --> 00:07:21,240
Wrap up and come over.

108
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,080
Okay.

109
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:27,430
If you don't want to talk, fine.

110
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,000
We've noted everything you said.

111
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,190
I'll ask Bai

112
00:07:31,830 --> 00:07:33,040
and see how his story differs.

113
00:07:33,310 --> 00:07:34,150
Wait.

114
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,560
What?

115
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,390
Want to talk again?

116
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:46,470
I know him.

117
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:48,230
Bai.

118
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:51,120
We first met at my shelter.

119
00:07:51,510 --> 00:07:53,040
He came to me.

120
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,750
The day I fell off,

121
00:07:57,190 --> 00:07:58,800
what were

122
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:00,680
Bai and Wang Li doing?

123
00:08:01,750 --> 00:08:03,800
They had a conflict.

124
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,000
I went to mediate.

125
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,630
Misunderstanding.

126
00:08:07,950 --> 00:08:09,160
The girl he abducted,

127
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:11,120
is she okay?

128
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:13,480
Good thing you caught him.

129
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,320
If he'd escaped,

130
00:08:14,340 --> 00:08:16,040
who knows how many deaths

131
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:17,710
would have

132
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:19,750
ended up on me.

133
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:24,400
Mediate?

134
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:27,310
Nice word.

135
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,150
- No, I...
- Li Xu,

136
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:31,870
if you want to talk properly,

137
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:33,870
think carefully.

138
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,910
I'll talk. Wait.

139
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,080
I'll talk.

140
00:08:41,630 --> 00:08:42,470
Officer.

141
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:44,630
I'll confess.

142
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,040
Officer Tang,

143
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,120
have you found Yimo?

144
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,510
To find her,

145
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:57,600
I need Bai first.

146
00:09:01,870 --> 00:09:03,630
Didn't you arrest Li Xu?

147
00:09:05,030 --> 00:09:06,360
He knows where Bai is.

148
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,720
He doesn't.

149
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:15,800
Wang Li,

150
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,910
tell me everything you know

151
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:20,790
about Bai

152
00:09:22,510 --> 00:09:24,630
and the Naked Banquet Case.

153
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,510
You want answers?

154
00:09:37,270 --> 00:09:39,270
Find Wang Yimo first.

155
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,480
She's in real danger.

156
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,440
You aware?

157
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,150
You know she's in danger,

158
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:53,440
and you still dragged her in?

159
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,390
That's how you're a father?

160
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:41,840
Tang Tang.

161
00:10:43,550 --> 00:10:44,390
Check this out.

162
00:10:45,390 --> 00:10:46,230
We've got evidence.

163
00:10:46,670 --> 00:10:48,200
This is the DNA comparison

164
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,600
Captain Zhao ordered earlier.

165
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,620
(Blood residue from the dog's nose
matches Bai Qiming's DNA)

166
00:11:03,740 --> 00:11:06,780
(Get to Zhaojia Village, south side.
Pickup in 3 days.)

167
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:10,270
Three days hiding there?

168
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:13,960
Those jerks at the Company.

169
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,350
They'd better keep their word.

170
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:21,260
(Police)

171
00:11:29,380 --> 00:11:30,620
(Serve the People)

172
00:11:33,020 --> 00:11:36,700
(Qingcheng Public Security Bureau)

173
00:12:03,390 --> 00:12:05,000
Stay safe, Wang Yimo.

174
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:07,630
If you get hurt,

175
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:09,030
you'll slow us down.

176
00:12:09,790 --> 00:12:10,790
What then?

177
00:12:14,790 --> 00:12:16,360
Caicai, help her up.

178
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,270
If she falls again,

179
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,560
you deal with it.

180
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:44,510
This suspect is extremely dangerous.

181
00:12:45,510 --> 00:12:47,320
Ensure the hostage's safety at all costs.

182
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:50,000
Three routes down the mountain.

183
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:51,480
Team One, due east.

184
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:53,150
Team Two, southeast.

185
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,630
Team Three, southwest.

186
00:12:55,030 --> 00:12:56,200
Grid search.

187
00:12:56,550 --> 00:12:57,600
Once spotted,

188
00:12:57,870 --> 00:12:59,080
report and close in.

189
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:20,710
Zhang.

190
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:22,960
Get people searching here.

191
00:15:24,150 --> 00:15:24,990
Got it.

192
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:45,040
Bring in the dog.

193
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:33,960
Bai Qiming.

194
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:35,870
Drop your weapon.

195
00:16:36,790 --> 00:16:38,150
You're surrounded.

196
00:16:40,550 --> 00:16:41,670
Don't joke with me.

197
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:43,360
Wang Yimo

198
00:16:44,510 --> 00:16:45,510
is in my hands.

199
00:16:46,390 --> 00:16:47,440
Give up.

200
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:49,600
You still have a chance.

201
00:16:54,390 --> 00:16:55,230
Move.

202
00:17:20,510 --> 00:17:21,550
Surrender.

203
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:24,270
You lost.

204
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:26,920
Tell your people to back off.

205
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,320
Or else,

206
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:29,830
I'll kill her.

207
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:31,070
Easy.

208
00:17:34,550 --> 00:17:35,680
Can we talk?

209
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,640
I won't repeat myself.

210
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:42,480
You want me to start

211
00:17:44,350 --> 00:17:45,480
with her eyes

212
00:17:46,030 --> 00:17:46,870
or

213
00:17:47,950 --> 00:17:48,790
her nose?

214
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:49,790
Okay, okay.

215
00:17:52,070 --> 00:17:53,030
Five steps back.

216
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:03,480
Bai Qiming,

217
00:18:06,750 --> 00:18:08,000
she has to live

218
00:18:08,350 --> 00:18:09,960
for you to bargain.

219
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:11,720
Do you understand?

220
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:13,200
Enough talk.

221
00:18:14,110 --> 00:18:14,950
Let me go.

222
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:17,680
If I die here today,

223
00:18:20,790 --> 00:18:22,000
she dies with me.

224
00:18:23,510 --> 00:18:24,510
Understand?

225
00:18:29,350 --> 00:18:30,440
Get me a car.

226
00:18:30,750 --> 00:18:31,590
No problem.

227
00:18:33,110 --> 00:18:33,950
Get him a car.

228
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:39,000
I got you a car.

229
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:40,440
Now release her.

230
00:18:41,510 --> 00:18:42,350
I'll take her place.

231
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:48,640
He wants to trade with you.

232
00:18:50,270 --> 00:18:51,110
What do you say?

233
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:53,510
Cut the act!

234
00:18:54,550 --> 00:18:55,830
Think you're better than Huahua?

235
00:19:02,110 --> 00:19:02,950
Tang,

236
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:05,030
don't worry about me.

237
00:19:05,590 --> 00:19:06,510
Shoot him.

238
00:19:06,510 --> 00:19:07,720
Don't let him go.

239
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:08,920
Shut up.

240
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:12,590
I'm done wasting time.

241
00:19:13,240 --> 00:19:14,110
Clear a path.

242
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:15,310
Get the car ready.

243
00:19:16,160 --> 00:19:17,680
If you play tricks,

244
00:19:21,310 --> 00:19:22,880
I kill her.

245
00:19:25,310 --> 00:19:27,750
Don't let him get away, Tang Tang.

246
00:19:33,480 --> 00:19:35,000
The cases you're working on

247
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:37,240
are done by me.

248
00:19:38,310 --> 00:19:39,790
Shoot him, Tang Tang!

249
00:19:41,240 --> 00:19:42,680
Shoot him, Tang Tang!

250
00:20:12,740 --> 00:20:17,100
(People's Police)

251
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:26,870
Did he confess?

252
00:20:27,030 --> 00:20:27,870
Yes.

253
00:20:28,310 --> 00:20:29,790
According to Li Caicai's testimony,

254
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:31,750
after escaping 15 years ago,

255
00:20:32,070 --> 00:20:33,920
Bai smuggled out through Yunnan.

256
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,480
Bai chose this place

257
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:37,550
and targeted Wang Li and his daughter

258
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:40,110
because Wang Li

259
00:20:40,110 --> 00:20:41,210
nearly killed him back then.

260
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:43,440
That hatred never faded,

261
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:46,110
especially after seeing

262
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:47,720
Wang Li's life

263
00:20:47,720 --> 00:20:49,030
was getting better and better.

264
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,720
He grew more twisted

265
00:20:50,830 --> 00:20:52,160
and reckless.

266
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:58,160
Fifteen years ago,

267
00:20:59,830 --> 00:21:01,590
Wang Li nearly beat Bai to death.

268
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:04,240
The killer at the scene

269
00:21:04,240 --> 00:21:07,160
Liu Yan allegedly witnessed

270
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:09,110
gotta be Wang Li.

271
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:13,790
Wang Li was tied to the Naked Banquet.

272
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:16,310
His accomplices were the kitchen staff.

273
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:18,720
How's Bai?

274
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:20,480
Bai?

275
00:21:20,830 --> 00:21:21,670
No vital injuries.

276
00:21:22,310 --> 00:21:23,790
After bandaging, he was fine.

277
00:21:23,790 --> 00:21:24,630
He's sent back later.

278
00:22:09,820 --> 00:22:10,850
System online.

279
00:22:26,400 --> 00:22:28,110
You haven't had it easy these 15 years.

280
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:30,680
How's the girl?

281
00:22:31,240 --> 00:22:32,080
She's fine.

282
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:34,750
Minor treatment at the hospital.

283
00:22:39,110 --> 00:22:40,880
You're confident.

284
00:22:41,550 --> 00:22:43,790
Shooting at me with a hostage.

285
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:45,440
More ruthless...

286
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:49,110
than I am.

287
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:55,880
You the Naked Banquet

288
00:22:58,400 --> 00:23:01,640
and coerced so many minors.

289
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:05,560
Oh right.

290
00:23:06,720 --> 00:23:08,240
We found Liu Xijun's body too.

291
00:23:09,160 --> 00:23:10,000
You did it, right?

292
00:23:10,830 --> 00:23:11,790
I mean,

293
00:23:12,000 --> 00:23:13,110
you ran for so long

294
00:23:13,590 --> 00:23:14,790
and still came back

295
00:23:15,270 --> 00:23:17,720
to take revenge on the Wangs.

296
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:19,270
You're the confident one.

297
00:23:25,590 --> 00:23:27,920
They got lucky.

298
00:23:28,350 --> 00:23:30,240
I ended up like this

299
00:23:31,030 --> 00:23:32,590
because of them.

300
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:34,550
If I had

301
00:23:34,550 --> 00:23:36,200
killed them back then,

302
00:23:37,350 --> 00:23:38,630
none of this would've happened.

303
00:23:41,550 --> 00:23:43,350
Ever heard of "reap what you sow"?

304
00:23:46,350 --> 00:23:49,110
We chased this case for 15 years.

305
00:23:50,030 --> 00:23:50,870
Bai Qiming,

306
00:23:51,550 --> 00:23:53,590
you really underestimated the police.

307
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:55,800
Come on.

308
00:23:56,160 --> 00:23:57,830
(Case Receipt)
Liu Xijun's autopsy report.

309
00:23:58,240 --> 00:23:59,510
Li Xu's statement.

310
00:23:59,880 --> 00:24:00,960
(Interrogation Record)
Li Caicai's statement.

311
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:03,310
The Naked Banquet Case.

312
00:24:03,550 --> 00:24:05,110
The murder of Liu Xijun.

313
00:24:06,110 --> 00:24:06,950
Do you confess?

314
00:24:07,350 --> 00:24:08,440
Liu Xijun?

315
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:14,200
He's just bones now.

316
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:16,350
How will you prove I did it?

317
00:24:17,070 --> 00:24:18,550
He had an asthma attack

318
00:24:18,790 --> 00:24:20,160
and was caught in a fire.

319
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:21,640
He brought it on himself.

320
00:24:21,640 --> 00:24:22,590
None of my business.

321
00:24:24,350 --> 00:24:25,210
Also,

322
00:24:25,270 --> 00:24:27,640
you never found

323
00:24:27,640 --> 00:24:29,070
the banquet venue back then,

324
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:30,560
right?

325
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:32,000
What about now?

326
00:24:33,550 --> 00:24:34,440
Found it yet?

327
00:24:37,790 --> 00:24:38,630
Well...

328
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:40,400
Everything on your desk

329
00:24:41,110 --> 00:24:42,350
is just speculation.

330
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:45,350
You don't have solid proof.

331
00:24:46,790 --> 00:24:47,920
You can't convict me.

332
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:51,520
You don't confess.

333
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,000
Fine.

334
00:24:57,110 --> 00:24:57,950
What about Liu Yan?

335
00:25:00,070 --> 00:25:02,750
She was your accomplice
in the Naked Banquet Case,

336
00:25:04,400 --> 00:25:06,590
and she witnessed your so-called death.

337
00:25:09,310 --> 00:25:12,790
So why was she poisoned
right after you came back?

338
00:25:14,020 --> 00:25:15,230
That's a hell of a coincidence.

339
00:25:15,880 --> 00:25:17,110
I also heard

340
00:25:18,240 --> 00:25:19,270
you met her many times

341
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:21,030
after returning.

342
00:25:23,030 --> 00:25:25,310
Her death has nothing to do with me.

343
00:25:27,310 --> 00:25:28,510
Ask Wang Li.

344
00:25:28,750 --> 00:25:29,590
Yes.

345
00:25:30,030 --> 00:25:31,240
You caught him, didn't you?

346
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:32,680
Go ask him.

347
00:25:32,790 --> 00:25:34,240
You mean

348
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:37,070
Wang Li killed Liu Yan?

349
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:39,110
Who else could it be?

350
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:43,550
Four months ago,

351
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:46,350
the first person I met after coming back
was Liu Yan.

352
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:50,160
I sent her to provoke Wang Li on purpose.

353
00:25:58,640 --> 00:26:00,270
Back then we all fell apart,

354
00:26:01,070 --> 00:26:03,400
he was the only one who walked away clean.

355
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:08,160
Lived comfortably for over ten years.

356
00:26:09,720 --> 00:26:11,240
Took zero responsibility.

357
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:13,960
Is that fair?

358
00:26:22,660 --> 00:26:25,140
(Welcome to Hongyun Restaurant)

359
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:26,790
While she was alive,

360
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:28,800
she was useful.

361
00:26:30,310 --> 00:26:31,270
But she's gone.

362
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:32,800
Doesn't matter.

363
00:26:33,220 --> 00:26:35,300
(Welcome to Hongyun Restaurant)

364
00:26:35,310 --> 00:26:37,440
Only Wang Li would kill her.

365
00:26:38,510 --> 00:26:39,830
As for the rest,

366
00:26:41,750 --> 00:26:43,200
come back

367
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:44,680
when you have solid proof.

368
00:26:58,460 --> 00:27:00,500
(Wang Yimo)

369
00:27:23,550 --> 00:27:24,510
Yimo, you're awake.

370
00:27:26,400 --> 00:27:27,310
My dad...

371
00:27:30,750 --> 00:27:32,790
You arrested him, didn't you?

372
00:27:35,920 --> 00:27:36,760
Yes.

373
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:42,200
What about Bai Qiming?

374
00:27:43,920 --> 00:27:45,000
That shot you fired.

375
00:27:45,750 --> 00:27:46,680
Did it kill him?

376
00:27:47,440 --> 00:27:48,280
No.

377
00:27:49,550 --> 00:27:50,440
He was injured,

378
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:53,030
but he's under control.

379
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:59,030
Get some rest.

380
00:27:59,960 --> 00:28:01,240
Call me if you need anything.

381
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:03,000
Tang Tang.

382
00:28:12,590 --> 00:28:13,430
I...

383
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:18,400
Can I...

384
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:24,160
Can I see my dad?

385
00:28:25,920 --> 00:28:26,880
Please.

386
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:30,400
Just once.

387
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:37,830
Sorry. I can't do that.

388
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:40,510
Get well soon.

389
00:28:50,180 --> 00:28:52,260
(China Police)

390
00:28:52,260 --> 00:28:55,780
(Criminal Investigation Team 2)

391
00:29:25,580 --> 00:29:27,220
(Hongyun Restaurant)

392
00:29:27,240 --> 00:29:28,350
Look at this.

393
00:29:28,440 --> 00:29:29,550
Hongyun Restaurant's

394
00:29:29,590 --> 00:29:30,850
been open for over ten years.

395
00:29:31,030 --> 00:29:33,000
How could something this big happen?

396
00:29:33,240 --> 00:29:34,270
No idea.

397
00:29:34,680 --> 00:29:35,720
Must be serious.

398
00:29:36,030 --> 00:29:37,340
A lot of cops.

399
00:29:37,340 --> 00:29:38,200
(Closed Until Further Notice)

400
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:39,040
Yeah.

401
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:41,270
What a shame.

402
00:30:03,750 --> 00:30:05,030
Zhang Ming never left.

403
00:30:05,240 --> 00:30:06,400
He's still here.

404
00:30:07,590 --> 00:30:08,550
Search again.

405
00:30:10,110 --> 00:30:11,400
If he's here,

406
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:13,720
we'll find him.

407
00:30:14,440 --> 00:30:15,280
Okay.

408
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:04,080
Liu, come on.

409
00:31:04,640 --> 00:31:05,480
This way.

410
00:31:17,030 --> 00:31:17,870
That mirror

411
00:31:18,310 --> 00:31:19,150
is huge.

412
00:32:13,750 --> 00:32:14,590
Something's up.

413
00:33:55,440 --> 00:33:56,280
He's still alive.

414
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:58,480
Tang Tang, look at this.

415
00:34:08,280 --> 00:34:09,550
Thank god Yimo's safe.

416
00:34:14,590 --> 00:34:15,430
Thank you.

417
00:34:16,550 --> 00:34:17,590
We found Zhang Ming.

418
00:34:18,800 --> 00:34:20,590
We went to Hongyun

419
00:34:20,590 --> 00:34:22,000
to look for Zhang Ming,

420
00:34:23,550 --> 00:34:25,320
but it ended up with a surprise.

421
00:34:28,670 --> 00:34:30,000
The second-floor mirror.

422
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:34,150
The Naked Banquet hall.

423
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:44,480
What did Zhang Ming say?

424
00:34:46,960 --> 00:34:48,110
He's still unconscious.

425
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:54,590
From the first time I met you,

426
00:34:56,320 --> 00:34:57,920
every time we spoke,

427
00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:01,400
I could tell

428
00:35:03,550 --> 00:35:04,440
you are

429
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:07,400
a very capable cop.

430
00:35:09,510 --> 00:35:10,760
And I can tell

431
00:35:12,150 --> 00:35:13,800
the day the truth comes out

432
00:35:16,190 --> 00:35:17,070
is very close.

433
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:23,960
Every case will be exposed.

434
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:27,440
Every hidden truth

435
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:28,920
will be revealed.

436
00:35:39,070 --> 00:35:39,960
I'll cooperate.

437
00:35:40,630 --> 00:35:41,710
I'll tell you everything.

438
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:44,280
I was the cook

439
00:35:45,000 --> 00:35:46,880
for the Naked Banquet.

440
00:35:48,510 --> 00:35:49,360
This knife

441
00:35:51,110 --> 00:35:51,960
was the one Bai used

442
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:55,840
to kill Liu Xijun.

443
00:35:57,960 --> 00:35:59,190
Why did he kill him?

444
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:02,320
There were candles that night.

445
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:06,070
One tipped over and started a fire.

446
00:36:07,230 --> 00:36:08,400
Chaos.

447
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:12,110
Liu Xijun had an asthma attack.

448
00:36:13,190 --> 00:36:14,630
He collapsed and couldn't move.

449
00:36:16,440 --> 00:36:20,000
Bai didn't want the venue exposed

450
00:36:20,030 --> 00:36:20,960
and

451
00:36:22,880 --> 00:36:25,550
he owed Liu Xijun a lot of money.

452
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:29,510
So he used the fire to silence him.

453
00:36:30,400 --> 00:36:31,800
Why did you kill Bai?

454
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:33,960
My daughter

455
00:36:36,070 --> 00:36:37,030
had leukemia.

456
00:36:37,670 --> 00:36:39,000
She was in the ICU.

457
00:36:39,510 --> 00:36:40,590
We need a lot of money.

458
00:36:41,190 --> 00:36:42,590
Bai promised

459
00:36:42,670 --> 00:36:43,510
to pay me.

460
00:36:44,710 --> 00:36:45,960
So I could save my daughter.

461
00:36:46,280 --> 00:36:47,710
But he didn't.

462
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:49,670
He delayed her treatment.

463
00:36:50,070 --> 00:36:52,000
Without the money, my daughter died.

464
00:36:53,230 --> 00:36:54,760
So I had to kill him.

465
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:04,760
Your real daughter

466
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:06,550
died of illness 15 years ago.

467
00:37:07,280 --> 00:37:08,280
Wang Yimo

468
00:37:10,190 --> 00:37:12,960
is Huahua,
one of the Naked Banquet victims.

469
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:18,030
How did you become her father?

470
00:37:20,320 --> 00:37:21,480
After my daughter died,

471
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:24,000
I was heartbroken.

472
00:37:24,960 --> 00:37:26,000
Even if Bai died,

473
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:27,320
my daughter wouldn't come back.

474
00:37:40,030 --> 00:37:41,510
Then I saw Huahua.

475
00:37:45,400 --> 00:37:46,240
I thought

476
00:37:47,510 --> 00:37:49,360
this was heaven giving me another chance.

477
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:52,360
A chance

478
00:37:53,550 --> 00:37:54,800
to be a father again.

479
00:38:00,550 --> 00:38:01,390
Officer Tang,

480
00:38:02,670 --> 00:38:05,590
I treated Huahua as my own child.

481
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:08,510
I would never let her touch crime.

482
00:38:08,510 --> 00:38:09,600
Never let her break the law.

483
00:38:09,710 --> 00:38:10,920
So,

484
00:38:10,920 --> 00:38:12,590
everything was me.

485
00:38:13,960 --> 00:38:15,320
Did you kill Liu Yan?

486
00:38:19,110 --> 00:38:20,400
Yes.

487
00:38:22,630 --> 00:38:26,070
Yimo is Huahua.

488
00:38:28,070 --> 00:38:29,070
Liu Yan threatened me.

489
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:31,710
She wanted money or she'd spill everything.

490
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:38,280
She was working with Bai.

491
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:43,590
I couldn't let her talk.

492
00:38:44,230 --> 00:38:46,110
I couldn't let her hurt Yimo.

493
00:38:47,400 --> 00:38:48,800
So I killed her.

494
00:38:52,280 --> 00:38:53,150
How?

495
00:38:53,840 --> 00:38:55,480
Poisoned sausage from the dog thieves.

496
00:38:57,320 --> 00:38:58,230
That's how she died.

497
00:39:19,710 --> 00:39:21,920
The chaos caused by the dog thefts,

498
00:39:22,590 --> 00:39:23,960
I was behind it.

499
00:39:24,510 --> 00:39:25,510
I wanted you

500
00:39:26,110 --> 00:39:27,230
to notice the shelters.

501
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,030
To notice Bai.

502
00:39:30,110 --> 00:39:32,030
If you already killed Liu Yan,

503
00:39:34,070 --> 00:39:35,840
why not kill Bai too?

504
00:39:36,710 --> 00:39:38,590
End it once and for all.

505
00:39:40,070 --> 00:39:41,190
From what I know,

506
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:44,480
after Bai came back,

507
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:45,840
you two met,

508
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:47,760
and many times afterward.

509
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:50,000
You had chances.

510
00:39:50,670 --> 00:39:53,440
Why be ruthless with Liu Yan,

511
00:39:54,030 --> 00:39:55,760
but hesitate with Bai?

512
00:39:56,030 --> 00:39:57,590
Killing isn't that easy.

513
00:39:58,880 --> 00:40:01,070
You know what Bai was like.

514
00:40:02,030 --> 00:40:03,840
He was far more dangerous than Liu Yan.

515
00:40:03,960 --> 00:40:05,550
If I failed,

516
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:09,880
Yimo and I would be dead.

517
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:12,190
So I waited.

518
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:14,630
I wasn't unwilling.

519
00:40:15,630 --> 00:40:16,470
Before I could,

520
00:40:17,960 --> 00:40:19,590
you guys stepped in.

521
00:40:31,630 --> 00:40:32,590
Your car?

522
00:40:33,590 --> 00:40:34,710
Blood on it.

523
00:40:35,280 --> 00:40:36,120
You hit someone?

524
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:37,920
Yes. That's my car.

525
00:40:37,920 --> 00:40:38,880
I hit a man.

526
00:40:40,030 --> 00:40:41,440
But he seemed fine.

527
00:40:41,630 --> 00:40:43,030
Are you sure?

528
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:50,510
Clear enough?

529
00:40:51,800 --> 00:40:52,920
You were driving.

530
00:40:53,110 --> 00:40:54,320
Yimo was in the passenger seat.

531
00:40:54,800 --> 00:40:55,640
What?

532
00:40:56,480 --> 00:40:57,760
You hit someone and fled?

533
00:40:58,270 --> 00:40:59,110
Here's what happened.

534
00:40:59,110 --> 00:41:00,150
I was driving.

535
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:01,920
After I hit him, I got out of the car.

536
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:03,110
I helped him up.

537
00:41:03,360 --> 00:41:04,880
I offered to take him to the hospital.

538
00:41:04,880 --> 00:41:06,510
He said he was fine

539
00:41:06,590 --> 00:41:07,710
and walked away.

540
00:41:08,760 --> 00:41:09,960
That's all.

541
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:12,070
At this point,

542
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:13,710
you're already sitting here.

543
00:41:13,960 --> 00:41:15,400
There's no point

544
00:41:16,150 --> 00:41:17,760
hiding anything.

545
00:41:17,960 --> 00:41:19,630
I understand.

546
00:41:21,110 --> 00:41:22,550
I admit the killings.

547
00:41:23,190 --> 00:41:24,360
Yimo is safe.

548
00:41:24,840 --> 00:41:26,630
I'm ready to pay

549
00:41:26,630 --> 00:41:27,470
for what I did.

550
00:41:28,070 --> 00:41:29,230
It's the price I owe.

551
00:41:29,710 --> 00:41:30,550
I accept it.

552
00:41:35,230 --> 00:41:37,030
I find Wang Li's confession strange.

553
00:41:38,070 --> 00:41:40,440
Since the dog thieves named Zhang Ming,

554
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:41,760
Wang Li's been

555
00:41:41,840 --> 00:41:44,070
our main suspect.

556
00:41:44,280 --> 00:41:45,960
But today,

557
00:41:45,960 --> 00:41:47,230
he confessed immediately.

558
00:41:47,230 --> 00:41:48,070
Too eager.

559
00:41:50,030 --> 00:41:50,920
What about Zhang Ming?

560
00:41:52,190 --> 00:41:53,030
He confessed.

561
00:41:53,060 --> 00:41:54,720
The dog thieves acted on Wang Li's orders.

562
00:41:54,960 --> 00:41:57,110
And 15 years ago, under Wang Li's direction,

563
00:41:57,110 --> 00:41:58,320
he and Xu Qiang

564
00:41:58,320 --> 00:42:00,000
(Interrogated: Zhang Ming)
worked as cooks for the banquet.

565
00:42:00,110 --> 00:42:01,070
He followed Wang Li

566
00:42:01,070 --> 00:42:02,190
for money

567
00:42:02,310 --> 00:42:03,630
to pay his mother's medical bills.

568
00:42:42,150 --> 00:42:42,990
Dad?

569
00:43:28,440 --> 00:43:29,280
Yimo.

570
00:43:30,920 --> 00:43:33,440
No matter how upset, you have to eat.

571
00:43:41,320 --> 00:43:42,360
Your dad's car

572
00:43:44,760 --> 00:43:45,880
has been impounded.

573
00:43:47,110 --> 00:43:48,150
That day

574
00:43:49,320 --> 00:43:50,400
can't be hidden anymore.

575
00:43:54,590 --> 00:43:55,800
Knowing your dad,

576
00:43:58,030 --> 00:43:59,710
he'll take everything on himself.

577
00:44:04,440 --> 00:44:05,280
Yimo,

578
00:44:06,440 --> 00:44:07,920
before the police uncover everything,

579
00:44:09,070 --> 00:44:10,000
I'll take you away.

580
00:44:24,440 --> 00:44:25,280
Yimo.

581
00:44:50,550 --> 00:44:51,390
Ms. Tong.

582
00:44:53,070 --> 00:44:54,550
You were born in winter.

583
00:45:00,630 --> 00:45:02,760
My dad got you a birthday gift.

584
00:45:08,070 --> 00:45:09,550
He can't give it to you anymore,

585
00:45:10,480 --> 00:45:11,670
so I'm giving it early.

586
00:45:12,960 --> 00:45:15,230
At least, it eases his heart.

587
00:45:18,630 --> 00:45:20,000
Bai Qiming's been caught.

588
00:45:20,760 --> 00:45:22,000
No one's threatening you now.

589
00:45:25,000 --> 00:45:25,840
Ms. Tong,

590
00:45:29,670 --> 00:45:30,710
I can't get away.

591
00:45:31,590 --> 00:45:33,230
But you still can.

592
00:45:35,920 --> 00:45:38,110
You never should've been dragged into this.

593
00:47:03,380 --> 00:47:07,940
(Repent and Reform)

594
00:47:22,180 --> 00:47:25,500
(Yimo)

595
00:47:29,260 --> 00:47:30,380
(Yimo)

596
00:47:39,400 --> 00:47:41,710
Stop moping and sighing.

597
00:47:52,030 --> 00:47:52,870
Stand up.

598
00:47:59,280 --> 00:48:00,550
A young, talented detective

599
00:48:00,630 --> 00:48:01,880
with a future ahead.

600
00:48:02,550 --> 00:48:03,710
Who trained you?

601
00:48:19,480 --> 00:48:20,320
You did.

602
00:48:53,220 --> 00:48:55,180
(Yimo)

603
00:49:02,480 --> 00:49:03,320
Yimo,

604
00:49:04,960 --> 00:49:06,760
when you see this video,

605
00:49:08,190 --> 00:49:09,150
I might

606
00:49:10,360 --> 00:49:12,400
never be able to be with you again.

607
00:49:14,230 --> 00:49:15,480
But it's okay.

608
00:49:16,670 --> 00:49:19,480
Only if I turn myself in

609
00:49:20,360 --> 00:49:22,280
will the truth come out.

610
00:49:23,150 --> 00:49:24,960
Only then can you truly be free.

611
00:49:26,920 --> 00:49:27,760
Yimo,

612
00:49:28,710 --> 00:49:30,480
let the past stay in the past.

613
00:49:32,230 --> 00:49:33,230
Look forward.

614
00:49:34,510 --> 00:49:35,630
In my heart,

615
00:49:36,360 --> 00:49:37,400
my daughter

616
00:49:39,590 --> 00:49:40,670
will always

617
00:49:41,760 --> 00:49:42,600
be bright

618
00:49:43,710 --> 00:49:44,550
and shining.

619
00:49:45,510 --> 00:49:46,630
You're amazing.

620
00:49:48,030 --> 00:49:49,960
You deserve a better tomorrow.

621
00:49:51,670 --> 00:49:53,000
I will always love you.

622
00:50:33,760 --> 00:50:35,360
Ride the Ferris wheel with me.

623
00:50:58,280 --> 00:50:59,840
What did my dad say to you?

624
00:51:02,150 --> 00:51:03,230
Did he say

625
00:51:04,280 --> 00:51:05,510
he did everything?

626
00:51:07,760 --> 00:51:08,670
He confessed.

627
00:51:16,670 --> 00:51:18,150
Remember the last time

628
00:51:19,030 --> 00:51:20,550
you met me for coffee,

629
00:51:20,630 --> 00:51:21,960
asking about my dad?

630
00:51:23,840 --> 00:51:25,230
I told you back then

631
00:51:26,920 --> 00:51:28,110
that he's a good man.

632
00:51:30,800 --> 00:51:31,920
A truly good man.

633
00:51:35,230 --> 00:51:37,110
Since the day I became his daughter

634
00:51:39,400 --> 00:51:41,880
he never let me suffer even a bit.

635
00:51:43,150 --> 00:51:44,360
He always wanted to protect me.

636
00:51:46,110 --> 00:51:47,400
Even now,

637
00:51:48,710 --> 00:51:49,590
I've grown up

638
00:51:50,110 --> 00:51:51,400
and made mistakes,

639
00:51:51,960 --> 00:51:53,030
and he's still the same.

640
00:51:58,110 --> 00:52:00,480
He just wants me to have a future.

641
00:52:08,110 --> 00:52:08,960
But…

642
00:52:10,630 --> 00:52:12,800
I don't deserve it anymore.

643
00:52:24,000 --> 00:52:24,840
I'm sorry.

644
00:52:26,630 --> 00:52:27,480
I lied to you.

645
00:52:30,960 --> 00:52:32,840
Zhang Ming and the dog thieves' handler

646
00:52:33,230 --> 00:52:34,070
was me.

647
00:52:35,630 --> 00:52:38,320
I put myself in danger again and again.

648
00:52:38,960 --> 00:52:40,320
I dragged you into this mess

649
00:52:40,960 --> 00:52:42,800
to get Bai on your radar.

650
00:52:43,960 --> 00:52:45,320
Back on the Shopping Street,

651
00:52:46,070 --> 00:52:47,880
you saw me call Zhang Ming.

652
00:52:48,440 --> 00:52:49,400
It was because I knew

653
00:52:50,230 --> 00:52:52,590
once the two dog thieves were arrested,

654
00:52:52,920 --> 00:52:54,110
they'd give up Zhang Ming.

655
00:52:54,630 --> 00:52:56,070
So I called to warn him.

656
00:52:57,280 --> 00:52:59,550
Later Zhang Ming got used by Bai

657
00:52:59,960 --> 00:53:01,320
and nearly dragged my dad down.

658
00:53:05,550 --> 00:53:06,760
I wanted to kill him.

659
00:53:10,960 --> 00:53:12,110
My dad went soft

660
00:53:13,110 --> 00:53:14,030
and spared him.

661
00:53:15,880 --> 00:53:16,840
He couldn't die.

662
00:53:17,710 --> 00:53:18,550
Dad.

663
00:53:26,510 --> 00:53:27,350
Ming.

664
00:53:29,000 --> 00:53:29,840
Ming.

665
00:53:32,360 --> 00:53:33,590
I won't kill you.

666
00:53:34,960 --> 00:53:35,800
But,

667
00:53:36,760 --> 00:53:38,590
you have to disappear for a while.

668
00:53:39,230 --> 00:53:40,510
When it's all over,

669
00:53:40,510 --> 00:53:41,690
I'll come back and let you go.

670
00:53:42,110 --> 00:53:44,670
If the police come for you,

671
00:53:44,960 --> 00:53:46,030
you tell them

672
00:53:46,280 --> 00:53:47,230
that everything

673
00:53:49,030 --> 00:53:50,150
was done by me.

674
00:53:50,840 --> 00:53:51,680
Understood?

675
00:53:52,880 --> 00:53:54,840
I'll take care of your mother.

676
00:53:55,280 --> 00:53:57,000
For life.

677
00:53:57,760 --> 00:53:58,600
I'll see her through

678
00:54:00,190 --> 00:54:01,440
to the end.

679
00:54:12,590 --> 00:54:13,440
And Liu Yan.

680
00:54:16,150 --> 00:54:17,280
I killed her too.

681
00:54:25,940 --> 00:54:27,700
(Welcome to Hongyun Restaurant)

682
00:54:27,700 --> 00:54:29,740
(Hongyun Restaurant)

683
00:54:35,150 --> 00:54:35,990
Who is it?

684
00:54:36,230 --> 00:54:37,280
Hello, ma'am.

685
00:54:39,140 --> 00:54:43,020
(Volunteer)

686
00:54:46,880 --> 00:54:47,760
Hi, ma'am.

687
00:54:48,110 --> 00:54:49,320
I'm a community volunteer.

688
00:54:49,550 --> 00:54:50,800
I brought you some supplies.

689
00:54:50,800 --> 00:54:52,030
Rice, flour, things like that.

690
00:54:52,710 --> 00:54:53,630
Volunteer?

691
00:54:54,550 --> 00:54:56,840
It's not a holiday. Why bring this?

692
00:54:57,000 --> 00:54:58,110
School program.

693
00:54:58,190 --> 00:54:59,630
We coordinated with the community.

694
00:54:59,960 --> 00:55:00,880
Just take it.

695
00:55:00,880 --> 00:55:01,850
If you need more,

696
00:55:01,870 --> 00:55:03,070
I'll bring'em next time.

697
00:55:03,880 --> 00:55:05,030
Next time?

698
00:55:05,230 --> 00:55:06,150
Well, that'd be nice.

699
00:55:06,150 --> 00:55:07,190
Put them there.

700
00:55:07,610 --> 00:55:08,670
I'll leave'em on the table.

701
00:55:09,590 --> 00:55:10,670
It's lunch time.

702
00:55:10,670 --> 00:55:12,000
Perfect timing.

703
00:55:12,230 --> 00:55:13,550
So this is your lunch?

704
00:55:14,000 --> 00:55:15,150
I actually brought my own.

705
00:55:15,590 --> 00:55:16,670
If you don't mind,

706
00:55:16,670 --> 00:55:17,760
we could share.

707
00:55:18,590 --> 00:55:19,430
Sure.

708
00:55:19,590 --> 00:55:21,190
But if you eat here,

709
00:55:21,280 --> 00:55:22,710
you clean up after.

710
00:55:22,840 --> 00:55:23,680
No problem.

711
00:55:25,110 --> 00:55:26,760
Does it suit your taste?

712
00:55:28,480 --> 00:55:29,550
Quite a spread.

713
00:55:30,230 --> 00:55:32,000
Here. Chopsticks.

714
00:55:33,320 --> 00:55:34,480
Eat more.

715
00:55:34,510 --> 00:55:35,800
And there's sausage too.

716
00:55:38,440 --> 00:55:39,280
Here.

717
00:55:40,000 --> 00:55:41,400
I'll clean up later.

718
00:55:41,480 --> 00:55:42,320
Okay.

719
00:55:44,920 --> 00:55:47,440
We never had volunteers
bringing food before.

720
00:55:48,400 --> 00:55:50,070
What's your name, girl?

721
00:55:52,230 --> 00:55:53,110
Wang Yimo.

722
00:55:54,550 --> 00:55:55,390
My nickname

723
00:55:58,760 --> 00:55:59,600
is Huahua.

724
00:56:08,840 --> 00:56:09,680
My dad

725
00:56:10,110 --> 00:56:11,070
is Wang Li.

726
00:56:11,710 --> 00:56:12,590
He runs a restaurant.

727
00:56:14,070 --> 00:56:15,280
Hongyun.

728
00:56:24,030 --> 00:56:25,400
You're the little girl

729
00:56:26,190 --> 00:56:27,710
I sent away back then.

730
00:56:29,070 --> 00:56:29,910
Yeah.

731
00:56:31,070 --> 00:56:32,550
You're the one who sent me.

732
00:56:33,550 --> 00:56:34,480
Remember now?

733
00:56:37,230 --> 00:56:38,480
Ma'am, don't stand.

734
00:56:38,480 --> 00:56:39,480
Eat a bit more.

735
00:56:39,760 --> 00:56:40,600
I'd say

736
00:56:41,480 --> 00:56:43,030
three to four minutes.

737
00:56:43,550 --> 00:56:44,800
Three or four minutes?

738
00:56:45,550 --> 00:56:46,480
What do you mean?

739
00:56:47,880 --> 00:56:50,280
See? You just wasted another minute.

740
00:57:01,150 --> 00:57:02,590
You'll feel the poison slowly.

741
00:57:02,590 --> 00:57:03,630
The pain it brings.

742
00:57:05,150 --> 00:57:06,070
Dying like this

743
00:57:07,110 --> 00:57:09,230
is mercy from heaven.

744
00:57:10,510 --> 00:57:11,590
You know exactly

745
00:57:12,480 --> 00:57:13,920
what you've done.

746
00:57:17,150 --> 00:57:18,800
The man Wang Li hit with his car.

747
00:57:20,480 --> 00:57:21,710
What did you do with him?

748
00:57:25,800 --> 00:57:26,960
We burned him.

749
00:57:32,320 --> 00:57:33,880
Do you know who he was?

750
00:57:43,000 --> 00:57:44,240
He was one of the businessmen

751
00:57:44,630 --> 00:57:46,480
at the Naked Banquet.

752
00:57:51,630 --> 00:57:52,710
I'll never forget

753
00:57:52,710 --> 00:57:54,710
his filthy eyes.

754
00:57:56,760 --> 00:57:57,760
My Huahua…

755
00:57:59,480 --> 00:58:01,150
I'll play with you.

756
00:58:02,230 --> 00:58:03,320
It was pure coincidence.

757
00:58:04,360 --> 00:58:06,030
He jumped out like a ghost.

758
00:58:06,670 --> 00:58:08,280
Like he was reminding me

759
00:58:13,030 --> 00:58:14,230
I'll never escape

760
00:58:15,590 --> 00:58:17,400
that nightmare.

761
00:58:28,070 --> 00:58:29,030
After he was hit,

762
00:58:30,280 --> 00:58:31,490
he wasn't going to live anyway.

763
00:58:33,510 --> 00:58:35,440
I wanted to finish him myself.

764
00:58:39,000 --> 00:58:40,360
But my dad stopped me.

765
00:58:43,320 --> 00:58:45,550
He couldn't bear
to see blood on my hands.

766
00:58:53,360 --> 00:58:55,280
I forced my dad to kill him.

767
00:58:57,360 --> 00:58:58,200
Tang Tang.

768
00:59:01,150 --> 00:59:02,510
It's all because of me.

769
00:59:11,710 --> 00:59:12,550
Huahua.

770
00:59:19,630 --> 00:59:20,470
I'm sorry.

771
00:59:24,000 --> 00:59:26,110
If I'd stopped Liu Yan
from taking you back then…

772
00:59:28,440 --> 00:59:29,880
if I'd been brave like you,

773
00:59:32,230 --> 00:59:33,880
standing up every time,

774
00:59:37,800 --> 00:59:39,230
none of this

775
00:59:39,710 --> 00:59:40,800
would've happened.

776
00:59:53,710 --> 00:59:54,800
Don't be stupid.

777
00:59:56,840 --> 00:59:58,510
Back then you were a kid too.

778
00:59:59,960 --> 01:00:02,110
You couldn't stop anything.

779
01:00:06,510 --> 01:00:07,800
I've hated a lot of people.

780
01:00:08,840 --> 01:00:10,280
But never you.

781
01:00:25,280 --> 01:00:27,630
So when the Ferris wheel reaches the top,

782
01:00:28,320 --> 01:00:29,960
you really can see the whole city.

783
01:00:37,760 --> 01:00:39,840
Life is strange sometimes.

784
01:00:41,320 --> 01:00:42,510
If it weren't for Liu Yan,

785
01:00:43,510 --> 01:00:44,840
I wouldn't have met my dad.

786
01:00:47,880 --> 01:00:50,150
He saved me

787
01:00:51,320 --> 01:00:52,160
at my darkest moment.

788
01:00:55,230 --> 01:00:57,670
He was a beam of light in my life.

789
01:01:00,960 --> 01:01:02,590
He gave me a second life.

790
01:01:04,590 --> 01:01:05,800
Now, because of me,

791
01:01:06,070 --> 01:01:07,150
he took it all on himself

792
01:01:07,760 --> 01:01:08,880
and fell back into the dark.

793
01:01:13,110 --> 01:01:15,480
And I don't deserve to stay in the light.

794
01:01:25,480 --> 01:01:26,320
Hello, Dad.

795
01:01:27,510 --> 01:01:28,510
I'm doing fine.

796
01:01:29,920 --> 01:01:31,710
Work's going great.

797
01:01:31,800 --> 01:01:33,730
My supervisor's offering me
a permanent position.

798
01:01:35,840 --> 01:01:37,320
Yes.

799
01:01:37,550 --> 01:01:39,590
I'm eating. Drinking water.

800
01:01:39,760 --> 01:01:41,070
Don't worry.

801
01:01:41,320 --> 01:01:42,710
I'll take good care of myself.

802
01:01:45,280 --> 01:01:46,630
Okay. You go ahead.

803
01:01:47,440 --> 01:01:48,280
Bye.

804
01:02:05,300 --> 01:02:11,780
(Hongyun Restaurant)

805
01:02:22,660 --> 01:02:25,060
(Hongyun Restaurant)

806
01:02:25,060 --> 01:02:27,880
♪Who is lured into the fall?♪

807
01:02:29,860 --> 01:02:32,290
♪A weeping believer♪

808
01:02:32,480 --> 01:02:35,530
♪Trades devotion for a gift♪

809
01:02:35,530 --> 01:02:36,940
(Dog theft methods; Buy a dog; Thieves;
Stirring crowds; Police)

810
01:02:37,430 --> 01:02:40,880
♪If the rules of this world♪

811
01:02:40,890 --> 01:02:43,710
♪Are written in blood♪

812
01:02:44,990 --> 01:02:47,470
♪Will you hold your obsession?♪

813
01:02:47,490 --> 01:02:51,230
♪Or kneel in the mud?♪

814
01:02:52,400 --> 01:02:54,350
♪Who is shameless? Who is pure?♪

815
01:02:54,350 --> 01:02:56,290
♪Who waits for a savior's cure?♪

816
01:02:56,310 --> 01:02:58,150
♪Who fights? Who yields?♪

817
01:02:58,150 --> 01:03:00,110
♪Who weaves the cage they cannot flee?♪

818
01:03:00,120 --> 01:03:01,940
♪When you pretend not to see♪

819
01:03:01,940 --> 01:03:03,940
(Liu Yan)

820
01:03:03,950 --> 01:03:07,180
♪No longer held captive by desire♪

821
01:03:07,580 --> 01:03:10,700
(Li Tong; Karaoke; Bai)

822
01:03:10,700 --> 01:03:11,540
(Karaoke Divas)

823
01:03:11,540 --> 01:03:15,120
♪Why does no one care about the truth?♪

824
01:03:15,140 --> 01:03:18,020
♪Who dares to gamble against fate?♪

825
01:03:18,020 --> 01:03:19,860
(Class of 1990,
Huaxin Middle School, Qingcheng)

826
01:03:22,700 --> 01:03:26,520
♪Why is my path covered in dust?♪

827
01:03:26,540 --> 01:03:30,300
♪Why is the horizon a barren land?♪

828
01:03:30,420 --> 01:03:34,410
♪Who can stitch a soul so torn?♪

829
01:03:34,420 --> 01:03:39,910
♪Who can return to the very start?♪

830
01:03:46,400 --> 01:03:47,240
Ming,

831
01:03:47,760 --> 01:03:50,150
have the dog thieves steal Maodou.

832
01:03:50,510 --> 01:03:51,440
Tell them,

833
01:03:51,440 --> 01:03:53,110
it must be sold to Bagong Dog Shelter.

834
01:03:53,650 --> 01:03:57,000
♪If the rules of this world♪

835
01:03:57,000 --> 01:03:59,910
♪Are written in blood♪

836
01:04:01,210 --> 01:04:03,660
♪Will you hold your obsession?♪

837
01:04:03,660 --> 01:04:07,790
♪Or kneel in the mud?♪

838
01:04:07,880 --> 01:04:08,740
Next weekend,

839
01:04:08,760 --> 01:04:10,800
go big on that online shop.

840
01:04:11,320 --> 01:04:12,960
Tell the owner you're in a rush.

841
01:04:13,000 --> 01:04:15,440
Once she confirms materials are in,
cancel the next day.

842
01:04:15,500 --> 01:04:16,590
(Who led Liu Yan to appear?)

843
01:04:16,590 --> 01:04:18,200
(Borrow money)
I'll send your commission later.

844
01:04:18,220 --> 01:04:20,120
♪Awakened in the deepest dark♪

845
01:04:20,120 --> 01:04:23,380
♪No longer held captive by desire♪

846
01:04:23,620 --> 01:04:27,430
Why are dreams torn to the bone?

847
01:04:27,430 --> 01:04:31,260
♪Why does no one care about the truth?♪

848
01:04:31,260 --> 01:04:35,320
♪Who dares to gamble against fate?♪

849
01:04:35,320 --> 01:04:38,580
♪And to flip the board?♪

850
01:04:38,820 --> 01:04:42,670
♪Why is my path covered in dust?♪

851
01:04:42,680 --> 01:04:46,500
♪Why is the horizon a barren land?♪

852
01:04:46,530 --> 01:04:50,300
♪Who can stitch a soul so torn?♪

853
01:04:50,300 --> 01:04:56,450
♪Who can return to the very start?♪

854
01:05:00,480 --> 01:05:01,320
Bai Qiming.

855
01:05:02,150 --> 01:05:03,110
I'm Wang Yimo.

856
01:05:04,360 --> 01:05:05,480
Let's meet.

857
01:06:03,190 --> 01:06:04,030
Comrades,

858
01:06:04,630 --> 01:06:07,590
in this cold-case crackdown,

859
01:06:08,000 --> 01:06:10,480
Team Two cracked the Nude Banquet Case

860
01:06:10,480 --> 01:06:11,880
and performed outstandingly,

861
01:06:12,000 --> 01:06:14,400
solving the bureau's longest unsolved case.

862
01:06:14,710 --> 01:06:16,440
Let's give warm applause

863
01:06:16,630 --> 01:06:19,840
to every member of Team Two

864
01:06:19,960 --> 01:06:21,020
for their dedication.

865
01:07:13,440 --> 01:07:14,280
Tang Tang,

866
01:07:15,110 --> 01:07:17,760
the case file's done.

867
01:07:28,800 --> 01:07:29,670
Zhao…

868
01:07:32,110 --> 01:07:33,960
Zhao must be happy.

869
01:08:08,260 --> 01:08:13,940
(Investigators: Zhao Fengcheng, Tang Tang;
Suspect: Wang Li)

870
01:08:30,460 --> 01:08:34,220
(Certificate of Honor)

871
01:08:35,350 --> 01:08:36,920
When I grow up, I want to be a cop too.

872
01:08:38,150 --> 01:08:38,990
Good.

873
01:08:39,560 --> 01:08:40,920
Then eat more fruit,

874
01:08:41,390 --> 01:08:42,310
get more sun,

875
01:08:42,390 --> 01:08:43,390
and take calcium.

876
01:08:43,720 --> 01:08:45,230
That's how

877
01:08:45,600 --> 01:08:46,680
you grow up strong.

878
01:08:48,880 --> 01:08:49,920
Here.

879
01:08:55,760 --> 01:08:56,600
Sweet?

880
01:09:26,600 --> 01:09:28,310
Baozi's up.

881
01:09:29,000 --> 01:09:30,070
Same as always.

882
01:09:33,600 --> 01:09:35,390
Zhao didn't come with you?

